At the newly unveiled Parliament Museum, the iconic pendulum symbolizes the passage of time — a reminder that while eras change, the spirit of democracy endures.
Standing tall in the Parliament House, it swings not just with gravity, but with the weight of centuries of leadership, decisions, and dreams.

An afternoon immersed in luxury, heritage, and craftsmanship.
Thrilled to have hosted an exclusive Hermès Masterclass, beautifully led by @puraskar from Elite Magazine, known for sourcing Hermès treasures from across the world for elite clientele.
From decoding iconic styles to exploring rare colors and customizations, it was a journey into the artistry that defines Hermès.
Proud that Queen’s Drive Club continues to create such meaningful collaborations, offering our members deeper experiences into the world of true luxury.

latestPosts.caption:
Unlocking the secrets of Hermès — one stitch, one story at a time.
ELITE Magazine, along with Essentia Homes, Queens Drive Club & Rimadesio, hosted the exclusive Hermès De-Coded Masterclass.
From the legacy of the Birkin to the elegance of the Kelly, guests explored the craftsmanship, forms, and finesse behind the world's most coveted bags.
Curated and presented by Puraskar Thadani @puraskar , Editor of ELITE Magazine — a true celebration of timeless luxury.

latestPosts.caption:
We enjoyed one-hour masterclass today on the iconic world of Hermès. @hermes @queensdriveclub @ritika_jatin_ahuja @shailykhera @puraskar 
It was quite an insightful session. Discussions were around : 
	•	The Legacy: Discovered the rich history and evolution of Hermès—from saddlery to global luxury icon.
	•	The Art of Craftsmanship: Learned what makes Hermès bags truly timeless and the details that define true luxury.
	•	Bag 101: Decoded the difference between a Birkin, Kelly, Constance & more.
	•	Investment Insight: Why Hermès bags are considered the most exclusive and high-value fashion assets.
	•	Spot the Real from the Replica: Key signs to identify authenticity.
	•	Styling Talk: How to style and carry your Hermès with flair.

latestPosts.caption:
A surreal moment for the Queens Drive Club as we stepped into the Parliament of India—where the soul of our democracy resides. Walking through these historic corridors filled our hearts with pride, purpose, and patriotism. It’s not just a visit, it’s a reminder that women belong in every room where decisions are made. Grateful for this honour and hopeful for the change we continue to drive.

#queensdriveclub #powerfulwomenempowerwomen #womenwithdrive #parliamentofindia #proudmoments #jaihind #womeninleadershiproles #heritageandhonor #indiathroughhereyes #drivingchange #womenempowerment #queensinpower #trendingreels

Today, we didn’t just drive — we made history.
Queen’s Drive Club at the Indian Parliament — a proud moment where passion met purpose, and horsepower met power.
A celebration of strength, sisterhood, and stories that deserve to be heard.
From city streets to the nation’s capital, the Queens continue to rise. 

#parliament #queensdriveclub #sisterhood #womenempowernment #womensupportingwomen #parliamenthouse #parliamenthouseofindia
